        super.viewDidLoad()
        webView.loadHTMLString("<font face='System 26.0'><html><body text=\"#C13735\" style=\'color=#C13735\'><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>tivovi IVS built the tivovi app(&ldquo;Serivce&rdquo;) as a free app. This Service is provided by tivovi at no cost and is intended for use as is.</p><p>Tivovi IvS will be referred to as (&ldquo;We&rdquo;), (&ldquo;Us&rdquo;), (&ldquo;Our&rdquo;) and (&ldquo;tivovi&rdquo;)</p><p>This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use and disclosure of personal information if you decide to use our service.</p><p>If you choose to use our service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to our privacy policy. The personal information that we collect is used for providing and improving our service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in the privacy policy.</p><p>We may develop new or offer additional services in the future. If the introduction of these new or additional services results in any change to the way, we collect or process your personal data we will provide you with more information.</p><p>With this policy we aim to enlighten you about:</p><ol><li>Make sure that you understand what personal data we collect about you, and the reasons for doing so.</li><li>Whom we share your personal data with.</li><li>Explain how we use the data you give us to improve and give you a formidable experience in tivovi.</li><li>Explain your rights and choices in relation to the personal data we collect and process your personal information.</li><li>How we will protect your privacy.</li></ol><p>With this we hope you understand our commitment to protecting your privacy.</p><h2>Information collection and use</h2><p><u>Directly from you</u></p><p><br /> <strong>Personal information</strong></p><p>For maximizing your experience of tivovi app you have to provide us with certain personally identifiable information, including but not limited to: Name, date of birth, gender, postal code, country, address, telephone number, e-mail, location, profile picture (taken directly from facebook if you choose their log-in option), user name and password, and your contacts.</p><p><strong>How we collect personal information</strong></p><p>tivovi may collect personal information you provide directly to us via mobile application, email, EDI, and other interactions. For example, when you register with us as a user for our services, participate in promotional activities, use our Service installed on a device, post on our Services or subscribe to notifications.</p><p>When you register as a user on tivovi, we will collect your registration details in order to create and process your or your organization&rsquo;s application and to administer the relevant accounts.</p><p>When you ask us to track a package for you, you give us the rights to use your personal information to find the tracking information on your appointed delivery service provider.</p><p><strong>Automatically collected from your use of our Service</strong></p><p>tivovi may automatically collect personal information for business-related purposes, which may include providing customer service, managing the services we provide, complying with legal requirements and for marketing our services.</p><p>When you use our app, we automatically receive information about which of our services you are visiting. This information will be stored anonymously, and we will used it to improve our service and to make our app more user-friendly, as well as statistical purposes.</p><p>Furthermore, we may automatically monitor all actions and behavioural movements derived from the use of tivovi app.</p><p><strong>Error data</strong></p><p>We want to inform you that when you use our service, we log data in case of error or crashes in the app. We collect this data and information solely for the purpose of correcting mentioned occurrence. This data may include information such as: Your device&rsquo;s internet protocol (&ldquo;IP&rdquo;) address, device name, operating system, operating system version, the configuration of the app, the time and date of occurrence and other statistics.</p><p><strong>Data derived from Companies and Organizations</strong></p><p>We gather information from companies and organizations on behalf of our users. All rights to data taken from companies and organizations are given to us by our users.<br /> We only take data, when our users ask us to.</p><p><strong>Access to Personal information</strong></p><p>In accordance with the applicable data privacy law, you may be entitled to request information about the personal data we have stored about you; to request certain access to, correction, deletion, portability or blocking of such data, and to request restriction of processing of data. <br /> <br /> tivovi reserve the rights to decline access or deletion of the information in case it is not required by applicable privacy law.</p><p>If you need your personal information updated or changed, you may log into your account and access your profile and information therethrough.</p><p>To avoid fraudulent requests to personal information, tivovi reserves the right to verify your identity by requiring sufficient personal identification.</p><p><strong>The right to object</strong></p><p>According to the General Data Protection Regulation Article 21, you have the right to object to the processing of your personal data, if we process your personal data on the basis of a legitimate interest, including for the purposes of direct marketing. You can lodge a complaint at the e-mail address: <a href='mailto:Privacy@Internetdanmark.dk'>Privacy@Internetdanmark.dk</a></p><p>To object to the processing; you may also have the right to file a complaint with the supervisory authority. For this purpose, or if you have any questions please contact; <a href='mailto:Privacy@Internetdanmark.dk'>Privacy@Internetdanmark.dk</a></p><p>More information about this right can be found particularly in the Article 21 of the General Data Protection Regulation No. 2016/679.</p><p><strong>Social media features</strong></p><p>tivovi enables you to use and share information with your social networks and interact with tivovi app therethrough. Your use of these social media networks in collaboration with tivovi may result in collection or sharing of personal information, depending on which Service you use. We encourage that you review the relevant social media network&rsquo;s own policies concerning this area, please do this to make sure that you understand the information that may be collected, used and shared by those sites. You may disable these functions at any time.</p><p>If you connect to the Service using credentials of a third-party Social Networking Site such as Facebook or Twitter, you authorize us to collect your authentication information, such as your name, e-mail address, and encrypted access credentials. We may store this information so that it can be used for the purposes explained in this statement, and it may also be used to verify your credentials with the Social media network. The information available to tivovi from a Social media network is affected by the privacy settings you establish at the Social media network. You understand and agree that a social media network&rsquo;s use of information they collect from you is governed by their privacy policies, and tivovi use of such information is governed by this privacy statement.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Service providers</strong></p><p>We may employ third party companies and individuals due to the following reasons:</p><ul><li>To facilitate our service</li><li>To provide the service on our behalf</li><li>To perform service-related services; or</li><li>To assist us in analysing how our service is used.</li></ul><p>We want to inform you, that the third party may have access to your personal information. The reason is to perform the tasks assigned to them on our behalf. However, they are obligated to never disclose or use the information for any other purpose.</p><p><strong>Links to other sites</strong></p><p>This service may contain links to other sites. If you click on a link, you will be directed to that site. Note that external sites are not operated by tivovi, and therefore we advise you to review the individual sites privacy policy, terms and conditions, contents and practices.</p><p><strong>Cookies</strong></p><p>Cookies are small packages of information used to analyse and track visitor&rsquo;s behaviour in order to deliver a tailored experience in content and functionality, with the user&rsquo;s point of view in focus.</p><p>tivovi have cookies installed in our digital channels. These cookies are used to gather information about, how you use our digital channels.</p><p>Third party may have access to our cookies, but solely for the purpose of increasing our visitor&rsquo;s experience in tivovi APP. Furthermore, all third parties may not under any circumstances disclose or use the information for any other purpose.</p><p>Cookies are protected in the same way as your personal information.</p><p><strong>Security</strong></p><p>tivovi wants to ensure high security for your personal data and have implemented relevant technical and organizational precautionary measurements to secure your personal data against unauthorized access, changes, public display, and deletion.</p><p><strong>Children&rsquo;s privacy</strong></p><p>tivovi does not offer our digital services to children and therefore does not knowingly store personal data about children. If you as a parent or legal guardian discover that your child has given us personal information, we ask that you contact us via e-mail: <a href='mailto:Privacy@internetdanmark.dk'>Privacy@internetdanmark.dk</a> so you may use your right to get your child&rsquo;s personal data changed or deleted.</p><p><strong>Changes to privacy</strong></p><p>Updates may occur to our privacy policy. Therefore, we advise you to periodically review changes on this page from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.</p><p><strong>Contact us</strong></p><p>If you have any questions regarding our privacy policy after reading this page or have any suggestions, you are more than welcome to contact us. <a href='mailto:Privacy@internetdanmkar.dk'>Privacy@internetdanmkar.dk</a></p><p>Tivovi IvS</p><p>Larsbj&oslash;rnsstr&aelig;de 3</p><p>1454 K&oslash;benhavn K</p><p>CVR &ndash; 38700669</p><p><a href='mailto:Privacy@Internetdanmark.dk'>Privacy@Internetdanmark.dk</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p></body></html>", baseURL: nil)
